%3D%5C%22005d41ce-8fe6-4e25-b188-8e49cbf88667%5C%22%3EThe%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20career%20experts%20agree%20being%20unemployed%20for%20too%20long%20can%20negatively%20impact%20someone's%20trajectory%20and%20make%20them%20%26quot%3Bunmarketable%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20are%20benefits%20to%20being%20more%20selective%20and%20patient%20in%20a%20job%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Watts%2C%20a%20career%20coach%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20community%20platform%20Teach.io%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20corporate%20culture%20that%20prioritizes%20profits%20over%20employee%20wellbeing%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bturn-off%26quot%3B%20to%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20young%20millennials%20favor%20organizations%20with%20ethical%20values%2C%20a%20commitment%20to%20diversity%2C%20and%20a%20transparent%20culture.%20They%20have%20witnessed%20the%20burnout%20that%20hustle%20culture%20can%20cause%20and%20aspire%20to%20something%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NEET%20mindset%20highlights%20how%20young%20people%20today%20are%20looking%20for%20work%20that%20truly%20inspires%20and%20fulfills%20them%2C%20not%20just%20jobs%20that%20pay%20the%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20Watts%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20workplaces%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaurie%20Cure%2C%20who%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20industrial%20and%20organizational%20psychology%20and%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20management%20consulting%20firm%20Innovative%20Connections%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20people%20who%20entered%20the%20workforce%20during%20a%20period%20of%20economic%20instability%20%E2%80%94%20after%20the%20Great%20Recession%20and%20COVID%20lockdown%20years%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bbore%20witness%20to%20many%20lows%20and%20very%20few%20highs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20living%20in%20a%20time%20when%20wealth%20is%20concentrated%2C%20home%20ownership%20feels%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20and%20rental%20prices%20and%20cost%20of%20living%20are%20skyrocketing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%20that%20are%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-rack-up-credit-card-debt-faster-millennials-genx-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtending%20with%20mounting%20debts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-hustle-generation-jobs-work-side-hustle-freelance-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20hustles%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20more%20appealing%20than%20a%20traditional%20career%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f344a76-b237-400e-95bc-fd4908067b05%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20about%20avoiding%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDarrin%20Murriner%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20the%20team%20coaching%20platform%20Cloverleaf%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20NEET%20label%20is%20not%20a%20retreat%20from%20work%20but%20%26quot%3Bperhaps%20a%20call%20for%20meaningful%20and%20fulfilling%20employment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20it's%20only%20articulating%20the%20demand%20for%20purposeful%20work%20that%20aligns%20with%20individual%20strengths%20and%20passions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20avoiding%20work%3B%20it's%20about%20finding%20work%20that%20lights%20a%20person%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-term%20impact%20may%20be%20that%20more%20people%20are%20in%20the%20right%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20are%20engaged%20in%20work%20that%20truly%20matters%20to%20them%2C%20they%20are%20more%20productive%2C%20innovative%2C%20and%20committed%2C%26quot%3B%20Murriner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPitcher's%20family%20doesn't%20understand%20his%20decision%20to%20be%20a%20NEET%20by%20choice%2C%20but%20he's%20found%20security%20and%20support%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20who%20have%20given%20him%20places%20to%20stay.%20This%20gives%20him%20faith%20that%20things%20will%20be%20OK%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20stopped%20caring%20about%20finances%20and%20stopped%20worrying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20hardest%20thing%20I've%20ever%20done%2C%20but%20also%20the%20best%20thing%20I've%20ever%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennial-neets-happy-idle-until-finding-right-job-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718876700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671495ced9a404d829e936e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennial-neets-happy-idle-until-finding-right-job-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20subculture%20of%20young%20NEETs%20%E2%80%94%20not%20in%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20or%20training%20%E2%80%94%20are%20happy%20to%20wait%20out%20unemployment%20for%20the%20right%20career%20path.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennial-neets-happy-idle-until-finding-right-job-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UGC-NET%20exam%20cancelled%20after%20inputs%20from%20I4C.%20What%20is%20it%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718876634000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111137175%2Cimgsize-1564908.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fknow-about-i4c-that-led-the-govt-to-cancel-2024-ugc-net-exam%2Farticleshow%2F111136020.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20widespread%20uproar%20over%20the%20NEET-UG%20and%20UGC-NET%20paper%20leak%20cases%2C%20the%20Indian%20cybercrime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C)%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20identifying%20potential%20loopholes%20in%20these%20entrance%20examinations.%20Operating%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Hom