Fmiddle-east%2Fdeath-toll-tops-1000-after-hajj-marked-by-extreme-heat%2Famp_articleshow%2F111136836.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Student%20Arrested%20In%20NEET%20Case%20Was%20Prepping%20In%20Kota%2C%20Was%20Told%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Sorted%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2022-year-old%20man%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20in%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20for%20medical%20college%20admissions%20has%20told%20the%20police%20that%20his%20uncle%20assured%20him%20the%20exam%20was%20in%20the%20bag%20and%20called%20him%20back%20from%20Kota%2C%20where%20he%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Yadav%20is%20among%20the%20four%20people%20arrested%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20paper%20leak%20case%20that%20has%20sparked%20nationwide%20protests%20and%20put%20the%20central%20government%20on%20the%20backfoot.%20A%20total%20of%2024%20lakh%20aspirants%20had%20taken%20NEET%20exam%20on%20May%205%20for%20admission%20to%20medical%20colleges%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20results%20on%20June%204%2C%20several%20irregularities%20emerged%2C%20triggered%20demands%20for%20a%20re-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%20to%20police%2C%20Anurag%20has%20said%20he%20had%20been%20preparing%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20at%20coaching%20hub%20Kota.%20%26quot%3BMy%20uncle%20Sikandar%20Yadavendu%20works%20as%20a%20junior%20engineer%20at%20Danapur%20municipal%20council.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20come%20back%20to%20Samastipur.%20He%20said%20'%3Cem%3Eexam%20ka%20setting%20ho%20chuka%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(exam%20is%20all%20sorted).%20I%20returned%20to%20Samastipur%20and%20my%20uncle%20dropped%20me%20at%20the%20home%20of%20Amit%20Anand%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20has%20said%20in%20his%20statement%20that%20Amit%20Anand%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20handed%20him%20some%20questions%20and%20answers%2C%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20memorise%20them.%20%26quot%3BThe%20next%20day%2C%20when%20I%20went%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20I%20found%20all%20the%20questions%20I%20had%20prepared.%20After%20the%20exam%2C%20police%20suddenly%20arrested%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESikandar%20Yadavendu%2C%20Amit%20Anand%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20have%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESikandar%20has%20told%20police%20that%20Amit%20and%20Nitish%20asked%20for%2030-32%20lakh%20rupees%20per%20student%20for%20the%20NEET%20question%20paper.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%20I%20have%20four%20students%20taking%20the%20test.%20Out%20of%20greed%2C%20I%20told%20each%20student%20that%20they%20need%20to%20pay%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20for%20the%20question%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20reportedly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20irregularities%20have%20surfaced%20in%20this%20year's%20NEET%3A%20as%20many%20as%2067%20students%20have%20scored%20720%2F720%20and%20six%20of%20them%20are%20from%20the%20same%20centre%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20high-cut%20off%20this%20time%20has%20left%20many%20students%20wondering%20if%20they%20would%20get%20a%20medical%20college%20seat%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20the%20high%20marks%20are%20a%20result%20of%20grace%20marking%20in%20some%20centres%20due%20to%20loss%20of%20time.%20The%20Centre%20and%20the%20NTA%20added%20that%20they%20had%20now%20cancelled%20the%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%201%2C563%20candidates.%20Amid%20reports%20of%20irregularities%2C%20a%20section%20of%20examinees%20are%20demanding%20a%20retest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718875800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fg60ba4pg_neet-protest_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-row-student-arrested-in-neet-case-was-prepping-in-kota-was-told-it-is-sorted-5930330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2022-year-old%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20in%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20has%20told%20police%20that%20his%20uncle%20told%20him%20that%20the%20exam%20was%20'sorted'%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20return%20from%20Kota%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-row-student-arrested-in-neet-case-was-prepping-in-kota-was-told-it-is-sorted-5930330%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-row-student-arrested-in-neet-case-was-prepping-in-kota-was-told-it-is-sorted-5930330%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-row-student-arrested-in-neet-case-was-prepping-in-kota-was-told-it-is-sorted-5930330%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Under%20Fire%20For%20Scrapping%20NET%2C%20Education%20Ministry%20Says%20Took%20Proactive%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20has%20said%20that%20the%20test%20was%20scrapped%20because%20its%20integrity%20may%20have%20been%20compromised%20and%20has%20emphasised%20that%20it%20won't%20hesitate%20to%20take%20action%20against%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20Jaiswal%2C%20joint%20secretary%20in%20the%20Education%20Ministry%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20exam%2C%20for%20which%20over%2011%20lakh%20students%20had%20registered%2C%20was%20cancelled%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20inputs%20received%20from%20the%20Indian%20Cyber%20Crime%20Coordination%20Centre.%20The%20exam%2C%20which%20was%20held%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20was%20cancelled%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%20A%20fresh%20examination%20shall%20be%20conducted%2C%20for%20which%20information%20will%20be%20shared%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20not%20hesitate%20in%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20wrongdoing.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20level%2C%20when%20the%20investigation%20is%20underway%2C%20we%20can't%20disclose%20more%20details.%20NTA%20has%20its%20own%20mechanism%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20stakeholders%20are%20involved.%20This%20all%20is%20under%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20which%20is%20under%20fire%20for%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20for%20admission%20to%20medical%20colleges.%20A%20total%20of%2024%20lakh%20aspirants%20took%20the%20exam.%20Reports%20of%20irregularities%20have%20now%20prompted%20nationwide%20protests%20and%20triggered%20demands%20for%20a%20re-test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20taken%20proactive%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20official%20also%20responded%20to%20questions%20on%20why%20the%20exam%20was%20conducted%20in%20OMR%20(pen%20and%20paper)%20mode%20this%20time%20--%20a%20shift%20from%20the%20earlier%20practice.%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20NTA's%20experience%20of%20four%20years%2C%20inputs%20were%20received%20from%20different%20stakeholders%20and%20this%20decision%20was%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUGC-NET%20is%20a%20test%20to%20determine%20a%20candidate's%20eligibility%20for%20the%20post%20of%20assistant%20professor%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20award%20of%20research%20fellowships.%20The%20Education%20Ministry%20yesterday%20ordered%20that%20the%20exam%20--%20held%20Tuesday%20--%20be%20scrapped%20after%20inputs%20that%20its%20integrity%20may%20have%20been%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20examination%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20protests%20against%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20has%20provided%20fresh%20ammunition%20to%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20target%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20ahead%20of%20the%20Parliament%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20described%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20NDA%20government%20as%20%26quot%3Bpaper%20leak%20government%26quot%3B.%20Other%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20including%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20have%20also%20slammed%20the%20government%20over%20the%20two%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718875740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fn7mjjlr8_net-exam_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-hesitate-to-take-action-against-anyone-education-ministry-on-cancelling-net-exam-5930027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20has%20said%20that%20the%20test%20was%20scrapped%20because%20its%20integrity%20may%20have%20been%20compromised%20and%20has%20emphasised%20that%20it%20won't%20hesitate%20to%20take%20action%20against%20anyone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-hesitate-to-take-action-against-anyone-education-ministry-on-cancelling-net-exam-5930027%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-hesitate-to-take-action-against-anyone-education-ministry-on-cancelling-net-exam-5930027%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-hesitate-to-take-action-against-anyone-education-ministry-on-cancelling-net-exam-5930027%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Burger%20King%20Murder%20May%20Be%20Revenge%20Killing%2C%20Mystery%20Woman%20Lured%20Victim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20chilling%20murder%20of%20a%2026-year-old%20man%20in