sibly%20with%20the%20dead%20man's%20phone.%20The%20woman%2C%20police%20have%20found%2C%20faces%20multiple%20cases%20in%20Haryana%20and%20had%20first%20come%20to%20Delhi%20to%20prepare%20for%20competitive%20exams%20and%20stayed%20at%20Mukherjee%20Nagar.%20Police%20suspect%20that%20she%20was%20part%20of%20the%20trap%20set%20up%20to%20lure%20Aman%20to%20the%20Burger%20King%20store.%20CCTV%20footage%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20woman%20took%20a%20train%20from%20GTB%20Nagar%20Metro%20Station%20to%20reach%20Rajouri%20Garden%20and%20after%20the%20murder%2C%20she%20took%20the%20metro%20from%20Rajouri%20Garden%20to%20Shakurpur%20Metro%20Station%2C%20PTI%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Gangster%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFugitive%20gangster%20Himanshu%20Bhau%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20in%20Portugal%20now%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20and%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20PTI%20that%20police%20suspect%20the%20same.%20Himanshu%20Bhau%20has%20said%20in%20the%20post%20that%20Aman%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20%26quot%3Bour%20brother%26quot%3B%20Shakti%20Dada%20and%20%26quot%3Bthis%20was%20revenge%26quot%3B.%20Warning%20the%20others%20involved%2C%20he%20said%20their%20%26quot%3Bturn%20will%20come%20soon%26quot%3B.%20Himanshu%20Bhau%2C%20whose%20gang%20operates%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%2C%20is%20notorious%20for%20extortion%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%20Bhau%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20jailed%20gangster%20Neeraj%20Bawana%2C%20fled%20the%20country%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Jhajjar%20Murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Bawana's%20cousin%20Shakti%20Singh%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Haryana's%20Jhajjar%20in%20October%202020.%20A%20police%20officer%20told%20PTI%20that%20Joon%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20tipped%20off%20rival%20gangster%20Ashok%20Pradhan%20about%20Shakti%20Singh.%20Himanshu%20Bhau%2C%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20wanted%20to%20get%20Joon%20outside%20his%20village%20so%20that%20he%20can%20be%20bumped%20off%20and%20the%20Burger%20King%20plan%20was%20made.%20The%20social%20media%20post%20by%20Bhau%20also%20mentioned%2C%20%26quot%3B14%20ke%20badle%2040%20goli%20di%20hain%20ginti%20kar%20lo%26quot%3B%20(40%20bullets%20in%20retaliation%20to%2014%2C%20count%20them)%26quot%3B.%20The%20authenticity%20of%20the%20social%20media%20post%20is%20being%20verified%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718875740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdv0mr1lo_burger-king_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-burger-king-murder-may-be-revenge-killing-mystery-woman-lured-victim-5929379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Burger%20King%20murder%3A%20The%20chilling%20murder%20of%20a%2026-year-old%20man%20in%20a%20shooting%20spree%20at%20a%20Burger%20King%20outlet%20in%20west%20Delhi%20may%20have%20been%20revenge%20for%20a%202020%20murder%20in%20Haryana%2C%20according%20to%20reports%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-burger-king-murder-may-be-revenge-killing-mystery-woman-lured-victim-5929379%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-burger-king-murder-may-be-revenge-killing-mystery-woman-lured-victim-5929379%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-burger-king-murder-may-be-revenge-killing-mystery-woman-lured-victim-5929379%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20fertility%20clinics%20are%20scaring%20young%20women%20into%20freezing%20their%20eggs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fertility%20clinics%20are%20targeting%20Gen%20Z%20%E2%80%94%20and%20young%20women%20are%20paying%20the%20price.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671d93fa76074d191cd087a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFertility%20clinics%20are%20taking%20to%20social%20media%20to%20tell%20young%20people%20the%20earlier%20they%20can%20freeze%20their%20eggs%2C%20the%20better.%20But%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case.%3Cp%3EAbanti%20Chowdhury%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Carney%20was%2026%20when%20she%20started%20seeing%20videos%20circulating%20on%20TikTok%20of%20women%20her%20age%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffertility-doctor-says-best-time-to-freeze-eggs-your-20s-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreezing%20their%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20began%20to%20panic.%20Was%20this%20something%20she%20should%20be%20thinking%20about%3F%20The%20Texas%20native%20was%20single%20at%20the%20time%20and%20had%20always%20wanted%20children.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%2018%2C%20I%20thought%20I'd%20be%20married%20by%2024%2C%20with%20my%20first%20kid%20by%2026%2C%26quot%3B%20Carney%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThat%20definitely%20did%20not%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20researching%20and%20found%20numerous%20articles%20preaching%20the%20advantages%20of%20freezing%20eggs%20before%20age%2035%20for%20higher%20viability%20in%20the%20future.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20the%20biological%20clock%20ticking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffroze-my-eggs-cost-risks-worth-it-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEgg%20freezing%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20a%20plan%20B.%20She%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20her%20fertility%20declining%20or%20rushing%20into%20a%20relationship%20with%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20she%20would%20have%20viable%20eggs%20to%20use%20whenever%20she%20found%20the%20right%20partner%20or%20decided%20the%20time%20was%20right.%20So%20in%202022%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2027%2C%20she%20discussed%20it%20with%20her%20primary-care%20physician%20and%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20fertility%20clinic.%20%26quot%3BI%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20it%2C%20but%20I%20will%20say%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20just%20freaking%20out%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarney%20is%20one%20of%20many%20young%20people%20who%20feel%20like%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-anthropologist-women-freezing-eggs-over-partnership-issues-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20out%20of%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ever%20since%20the%20American%20Society%20for%20Reproductive%20Medicine%20lifted%20the%20%26quot%3Bexperimental%26quot%3B%20tag%20from%20egg%20freezing%20in%202012%2C%20more%20people%20have%20decided%20to%20freeze%20their%20eggs.%20Between%202012%20and%202020%2C%20procedures%20surged%20by%20400%25%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Society%20for%20Assisted%20Reproductive%20Technology.%20Initially%2C%20ASRM%20recommended%20egg%20freezing%20only%20for%20women%20undergoing%20medical%20treatments%20that%20affected%20their%20fertility%2C%20but%20in%202021%2C%20thanks%20to%20improved%20technology%2C%20ASRM%20acknowledged%20%26quot%3Bdelaying%20childbearing%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20valid%20reason%20for%20the%20procedure.%20And%20in%202022%2C%20women%20were%20given%20the%20option%20to%20store%20their%20eggs%20for%20up%20to%2055%20years%2C%20a%20significant%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%2010-year%20limit.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20egg%20freezing%20was%20an%20option%20for%20younger%20women%20worried%20about%20their%20reproductive%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20clinics%20have%20used%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20to%20entice%20an%20increasingly%20young%20base%20of%20women%20with%20the%20message%20that%20they're%20running%20out%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20the%20earlier%20you%20freeze%20your%20eggs%2C%20the%20better%2C%20they%20warn.%20From%202021%20to%202022%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20year%20for%20which%20data%20is%20available%2C%20US%20egg-freezing%20procedures%20jumped%20another%2020%25%2C%20to%20nearly%2030%2C000.%20Younger%20and%20younger%20women%20are%20posting%20online%20about%20freezing%20their%20eggs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20getting%20paid%20by%20clinics%20to%20do%20it.%20But%20the%20messaging%20often%20ignores%20a%20few%20key%20realities%3A%20Egg%20freezing%20is%20expensive%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20success%20vary%20significantly%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20earlier%20is%20always%20better%20isn't%20clearly%20supported%20by%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEgg%20freezing%20is%20a%20really%20valuable%20and%20important%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Zeynep%20Gurtin%2C%20a%20sociologist%20and%20lecturer%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Women's%20Health%20at%20University%20College%20London%2C%20told%20me.%20However%2C%20she%20said%20it's%20not%20a%20blanket%20positive.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20starting%20to%20see%20with%20egg%20freezing%20now%20is%20the%20overexploitation%20of%20egg%20freezing%20as%20a%20technology%20that's%20marketed%20as%20being%20potentially%20useful%20to%20all%20women%20who%20should%20use%20it%20as%20some%20kind%20of%20backup%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurtin%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20absolutely%20not%20what%20this%20technology%20is%20designed%20for%20or%20is%20right%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20in%20Carney's%20egg-freezing%20journey%20was%20to%20go%20on%20birth%20control%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20had%20never%20done%20before.%20%26quot%3BThat%20week%2C%20I%20was%20a%20raging%20bitch%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20pill%20sent%20her%20emotions%20spiraling%20in%20every%20direction.%20Then%2C%20Carney%20had%20to%20self-inject%20daily%20hormone%20shots%20for%2010%20days%20to%20coax%20her%20ovaries%20to%20mature%20as%20many%20eggs%20as%20possible.%20Finally%2C%20the%20doctor%20could%20remove%20her%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20typical%20egg-retrieval%20procedure%2C%20a%20doctor%20guides%20a%20needle%20attached%20to%20a%20catheter%20through%20the%20vaginal%20wall%20and%20draws%20out%20the%20eggs%20using%20light%20suction%20while%20the%20patient%20is%20under%20anesthesia.%20The%20harvested%20eggs%20are%20immediately%20preserved%20in%20a%20cryogenic%20freezer%20in%20liquid%20nitrogen%2C%20where%20they%20stay%20until%20they're%20needed%20for%20in%20vitro%20fertilization.%20The%20whole%20procedure%20takes%20less%20than%2020%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20but%20recovering%20from%20the%20anesthesia%20might%20take%20several%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20eggs%20the%20doctor%20can%20retrieve%2C%20the%20better%20the%20chance%20one%20will%20result%20in%20a%20successful%20pregnancy%20down%20the%20road.%20In%20a%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fertstert.org%2Farticle%2FS0015-0282(22)00254-0%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20women%20who%20froze%20their%20eggs%20before%20the%20age%20of%2038%20had%20a%2070%25%20chance%20of%20having%20a%20baby%20if%20they%20thawed%2020%20or%20more%20eggs.%20But%20if%20they%20thawed%20fewer%20than%2010%20eggs%2C%20the%20success%20rate%20plunged%20to%2036%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20under%2038%20typically%20get%2010%20to%2020%20eggs%20per%20retrieval%2C%20but%20of%20the%20eggs%20that%20are%20frozen%2C%20not%20all%20will%20survive%20the%20thawing%20process.%20Even%20fewer%20will%20be%20successfully%20fertilized%2C%20fewer%20still%20will%20become%20embryos%2C%20and%20even%20fewer%20will%20result%20in%20a%20live%20birth.%20At%20each%20stage%20of%20the%20process%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20that%20something%20goes%20wrong.%20%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20best-case%20scenario%2C%20your%20success%20rate%20is%20never%20going%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20the%20average%20IVF%20cycle%2C%20which%20is%20around%2030%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurtin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarney's%20retrieval%20resulted%20in%20only%20nine%20eggs.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20get%20a%20lot%20more%20because%20I%20was%2027%20and%20very%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BSome%20women%20get%2C%20like%2C%2025%20to%2030.%26quot%3B%20She%20felt%20frustrated%20and%20discouraged.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20did%20all%20that%20and%20now%20I%20only%20have%20nine%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled%20thinking%20at%20the%20time.%20Most%20women%20undergo%20the%20entire%20process%20multiple%20times%20to%20retrieve%20more%20eggs%20and%20increase%20their%20chances%20of%20success.%20But%20that%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Carney%20doesn't%20plan%20to%20do%20another%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F39-year-old-woman-spent-6000-on-egg-retrieval-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEgg%20retrieval%3C%2Fa%3E%20typically%20runs%20you%20%248%2C000%20per%20procedure%2C%20plus%20%242%2C000%20to%20%245%2C000%20for%20the%20hormone%20shots.%20Each%20year%20you%20store%20your%20eggs%2C%20you%20also%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20fee%20ranging%20from%20%24400%20to%20%24800.%20And%20when%20you%20decide%20to%20use%20your%20eggs%2C%20it%20costs%20%243%2C000%20to%20%245%2C000%20for%20the%20frozen-embryo%20transfer.%20Insurance%20coverage%20for%20these%20procedures%20is%20rare%2C%20with%20exceptions%20in%20situations%20such%20as%20when%20a%20cancer%20patient's%20fertility%20is%20endangered%20by%20chemotherapy.%20Some%20employers%20do%20offer%20assistance%20%E2%80%94%20Meta%20and%20Apple%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20cover%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20for%20egg%20freezing%2C%20and%20since%202016%2C%20active-duty%20women%20in%20the%20US%20military%20can%20have%20the%20procedure%20covered%20%E2%80%94%20but%20everyone%20else%20is%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20pay%20for%20her%20procedure%2C%20Carney%20took%20out%20a%20%246%2C000%20loan.%20Her%20insurance%20covered%20a%20couple%20of%20doctor%20visits%2C%20and%20her%20mother%20helped%20out%20with%20an%20extra%20%242%2C000%20to%20%243%2C000%20for%20the%20hormone%20treatments.%20Carney%20now%20pays%20%24200%20each%20month%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20loan%2C%20and%20when%20we%20last%20spoke%2C%20she%20had%20just%20paid%20her%20annual%20%24600%20fee%20to%20keep%20the%20eggs%20frozen.%20She%20plans%20to%20keep%20paying%20until%20she%20turns%2036%3B%20if%20she%20hasn't%20used%20them%20by%20then%2C%20she'll%20have%20them%20destroyed%20to%20avoid%20paying%20more%20fees.%20Nine%20years%20of%20storage%20would%20bring%20her%20total%20cost%20to%20nearly%20%2414%2C500%2C%20not%20including%20interest%20on%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20freezing%20eggs%20doesn't%20guarantee%20children%2C%20it's%20also%20not%20clear%20whether%20doing%20the%20procedure%20in%20your%2020s%20gives%20you%20a%20significant%20advantage%20for%20a%20successful%20pregnancy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7894970%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMost%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fepdf%2F10.1007%2Fs10815-020-01791-w%3Fsharing_token%3D5aJMPlNNTd2Lpy55EKMYUfe4RwlQNchNByi7wbcMAY52MkJi-03fy3R8QlAUPDUXI7F-oi_YXVldV0sf3AKhF6vLMpipo1fUorXJhOToCt5qlLs07g20-OrtikK0T3uGl7gWuuwJnFR_oK_wErpuO9oyTnBD-c-caiJgQ7uj3YE%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20compare%20women%20in%20their%20early%2030s%20with%20those%20in%20their%20late%2030s%20and%20early%2040s.%20In%20those%20studies%2C%20women%20under%2035%20tended%20to%20have%20better%20outcomes%20than%20those%20who%20froze%20their%20eggs%20at%2040%20or%20later.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20earlier%20is%20always%20better.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10342811%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOther%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F25881876%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20found%20that%20there%20isn't%20much%20added%20benefit%20to%20freezing%20eggs%20earlier%20than%2030.%20One%202015%20paper%20looked%20at%20the%20optimal%20time%20to%20freeze%20eggs%20among%20women%2025%20to%2040.%20It%20found%20that%20freezing%20your%20eggs%20before%20your%2030s%20didn't%20generally%20improve%20your%20chances%20of%20having%20a%20live%20birth%20over%20trying%20naturally.%20While%20egg%20freezing%20has%20the%20highest%20chance%20of%20success%20when%20done%20before%2035%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20the%20age%20at%20which%20freezing%20your%20eggs%20made%20the%20most%20sense%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20viability%20and%20cost-effectiveness%20was%2037.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20generally%20recommend%20women%20who%20are%20considering%20freezing%20their%20eggs%20do%20so%20before%20the%20age%20of%2035%20if%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Geeta%20Nargund%2C%20the%20medical%20director%20of%20the%20fertility%20center%20ABC%20IVF%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20no%20medical%20reason%20to%20freeze%20your%20eggs%20in%20your%2020s%2C%20I%20would%20advise%20that%20you%20would%20be%20in%20a%20better%20position%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20decision%20in%20your%20early%2030s%20instead%2C%20while%20the%20chances%20of%20success%20of%20treatment%20remain%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20chance%20that%20someone%20never%20uses%20their%20frozen%20eggs.%20In%20fact%2C%20very%20few%20women%20do%20%E2%80%94%20only%2016%25%20of%20women%20who%20froze%20their%20eggs%20at%20one%20London%20hospital%20between%20January%202016%20and%20March%202022%20came%20back%20to%20use%20them%2C%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10342811%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20It's%20another%20reason%20earlier%20isn't%20always%20better%3A%20In%20your%2020s%2C%20you%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20runway.%20The%20right%20partner%20might%20be%20around%20the%20next%20corner%2C%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20conceiving%20naturally%2C%20time%20is%20on%20your%20side.%20More%20women%20are%20having%20children%20into%20their%20late%2030s%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20reaches%20that%20point%20and%20still%20doesn't%20see%20kids%20in%20their%20immediate%20future%2C%20there's%20still%20time%20to%20explore%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%2027-year-old%20doesn't%20need%20to%20feel%20like%20she's%20left%20behind%20or%20left%20out%20because%20she's%20not%20freezing%20her%20eggs%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurtin%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%2C%20most%20women%2C%20let%20alone%20women%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20are%20not%20freezing%20their%20eggs%2C%20don't%20need%20to%20freeze%20their%20eggs%2C%20and%20don't%20need%20to%20think%20about%20freezing%20their%20eggs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFertility%20clinics%20have%20an%20obvious%20business%20case%20for%20trying%20to%20convince%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%20that%20egg%20freezing%20is%20something%20they%20should%20do.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7732876%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Emily%20Tiemann%2C%20then%20a%20regulatory-policy%20manager%20at%20the%20Human%20Fertilisation%20and%20Embryology%20Authority%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20dug%20into%20the%20marketing%20strategies%20of%20egg-freezing%20companies.%20First%2C%20she%20noticed%20a%20significant%20lack%20of%20comprehensive%20information%20on%20egg-freezing%20sites.%20Second%2C%20she%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20language%20used%2C%20which%20seemed%20to%20target%20young%20women%20at%20a%20particular%20stage%20in%20their%20lives.%20Phrases%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Byou%20haven't%20found%20the%20right%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Byou're%20waiting%20for%20Mr.%20Right%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Byou%20want%20to%20take%20control%20of%20your%20life%26quot%3B%20were%20common%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20kinds%20of%20messages%20that%20you%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20think%20would%20be%20on%20a%20clinical%20site%20that%20offers%20medical%20treatment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20marketing%20toward%20younger%20women%20has%20amped%20up.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fertility-startup-kindbody-began-working-with-employers-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKindbody%2C%20a%20venture-backed%20egg-freezing%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20launched%20its%20first%20%26quot%3Bboutique%26quot%3B%20clinic%20in%20New%20York%20City%20in%202018%2C%20traveled%20nationwide%20in%202020%20with%20an%20Instagram-friendly%20van%20providing%20complimentary%20hormone%20tests%20to%20check%20fertility%20and%20marketing%20its%20services.%20Another%20well-known%20fertility%20studio%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fegg-freezing-nyc-trellis-fertility-studio-clinic-photos-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrellis%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calls%20itself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Equinox%20of%20egg%20freezing%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20%24385-a-month%20luxury%20gym%20chain%20popular%20among%20millennials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20companies%20have%20partnered%20with%20social-media%20stars%20to%20leverage%20their%20reach.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstories%2Fhighlights%2F17851263305348542%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlex%20Stewart%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20influencer%20who%20was%2035%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20offered%20a%20significant%20discount%20by%20the%20fertility-preservation%20program%20Ova%20to%20share%20her%20experience%20with%20her%20Instagram%20and%20podcast%20audiences.%20Similarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fserenakerrigan%2Fp%2FC3GWOw5J7_K%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESerena%20Kerrigan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20content%20creator%2C%20decided%20to%20freeze%20her%20eggs%20with%20Spring%20Fertility%20in%20New%20York%20after%20it%20approached%20her%20for%20a%20paid%20Instagram%20collaboration.%20Other%20companies%20have%20targeted%20women%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flaivfclinic.com%2Fblog%2Fbenefits-of-freezing-my-eggs-in-my-20s%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40freezebyco%2Fvideo%2F7188974362983255342%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial-media%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tout%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20children%20on%20YOUR%20time%26quot%3B%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20feel%20you%20have%20to%20rush%20into%20a%20relationship%20this%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Carney%20began%20exploring%20fertility%20services%2C%20she%20couldn't%20ignore%20the%20targeted%20ads%20that%20followed%20her%20everywhere%2C%20recalling%20ones%20featuring%20the%20popular%20reality-TV%20star%20Lala%20Kent.%20Carney%20also%20documented%20her%20own%20journey%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40brennacarney3%2Fvideo%2F7215376131204222254%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20women%20who%20use%20their%20eggs%20are%20in%20their%20late%2030s%2C%20clinics%20make%20money%20on%20the%20prolonged%20storage%20times.%20%26quot%3BThe%20earlier%2C%20the%20more%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Tiemann%20put%20it.%20In%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffertility-startups-booming-despite-market-downturn-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efertility-tech%20startups%20raised%20%24855%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20jump%20from%20the%20%24306%20million%20raised%20in%202017.%20And%20in%20fiscal%20year%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexclusive-kindbody-fertility-startup-raising-30-million-fertility-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKindbody%3C%2Fa%3E%20grew%20its%20revenue%20by%2050%25%20to%20about%20%24180%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoojin%20Jang%2C%20now%2032%2C%20said%20she%20regretted%2