6b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20working%20at%20Twin%20Peaks%2C%20I%20was%20young%20and%20extremely%20shy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20grateful%20for%20my%20first%20few%20years%20at%20Twin%20Peaks.%20I%20started%20to%20break%20out%20of%20my%20shell%2C%20felt%20confident%2C%20and%20made%20a%20good%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20got%20older%2C%20my%20body%20and%20mindset%20changed.%20The%20Twin%20Peaks%20in%20Tennessee%2C%20where%20I%20worked%2C%20valued%20the%20size%20of%20my%20pants%20over%20my%20work%20ethic.%20I%20also%20briefly%20worked%20at%20a%20Twin%20Peaks%20location%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20same.%20There's%20a%20franchise%20standard%20for%20working%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20and%20managers%20commented%20on%20my%20weight%20and%20other%20women's%20appearances%2C%20which%20felt%20demeaning.%20I%20told%20myself%20it%20was%20what%20I%20signed%20up%20for%20since%20I%20signed%20a%20waiver%20to%20be%20a%20model%20there%20(hostesses%2C%20servers%2C%20and%20bartenders%20are%20considered%20%26quot%3Bmodels%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%2C%20my%20brother%20died%2C%20and%20I%20barely%20ate%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fwhat-is-depression%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edepressed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20was%20tiny.%20My%20body%20started%20changing%20as%20I%20got%20healthier%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20lose%20weight%20to%20keep%20my%20job.%20I%20began%20to%20struggle%20with%20an%20eating%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hit%20a%20breaking%20point%20in%202020.%20Working%20at%20Twin%20Peaks%20helped%20me%20pay%20my%20way%20through%20college%2C%20but%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20venture%20out%20in%20my%20career.%20I%20quit%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad02b728-9fe9-428c-a662-a7c2109719be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20started%20taking%20marketing%20classes%20