nd%20underground%20saline%20water%20for%20these%20purposes%2C%20especially%20in%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%20where%20groundwater%20quality%20is%20infamously%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F98_-of-the-water-used-in-a-household-is-recyclable-1-1718870042.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greywater%20vs%20blackwater%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20what%20greywater%20is%2C%20Mukherjee%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20use%20freshwater%20in%20our%20taps%20or%20from%20our%20collection%20tank%2C%20it%20is%20typically%20divided%20into%20two%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346189%2Fjalsevak-pune-startup-engineer-abhijt-sathe-recycles-greywater-bengaluru-water-crirs-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esewage%20water%20and%20greywater.%20%3C%2Fa%3ESewage%20water%20comes%20from%20flushing%20toilets%2C%20while%20greywater%20originates%20from%20all%20other%20activities%2C%20such%20as%20taking%20baths%2C%20washing%20clothes%2C%20washing%20utensils%2C%20mopping%20the%20floor%2C%20and%20any%20other%20activities%20that%20do%20not%20involve%20sewage%20or%20urine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20black%20water%2C%20which%20contains%20sewage%20and%20toilet%20waste%2C%20greywater%20is%20relatively%20clean%20and%20can%20be%20recycled%20for%20various%20non-potable%20uses%2C%20such%20as%20irrigation%2C%20flushing%20toilets%2C%20and%20landscape%20watering.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThere%20are%20many%20cost-effective%20filtration%20methods%20with%20a%201%2C000-litre%20capacity.%20This%20is%20enough%20for%20every%20family%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352664%2Fwater-treatment-plants-dig