ll%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExactly%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20a%20story%20with%20this%20headline%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20day%20Denmark%20stood%20still%3A%20Christian%20Eriksen's%20collapse%20and%20the%20heroes%20who%20saved%20him.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2012%2C%202021%2C%20Denmark%20faced%20Finland%20in%20a%20match%20in%20the%202020%20Euro%20tournament.%20In%20the%2043rd%20minute%2C%20the%20world%20witnessed%20a%20shock%20as%20Denmark's%20midfielder%20collapsed%20on%20the%20pitch%20for%20reasons%20then%20unknown.%20Realising%20something%20was%20terribly%20wrong%2C%20fellow%20players%20rushed%20to%20ensure%20that%20his%20airway%20remained%20open.%20The%20team%20doctor%20feared%20the%20worst%20-%20Eriksen%20had%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20on%20the%20pitch.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20lay%20on%20the%20pitch%20for%20a%20tense%2013%20minutes%20before%20somehow%20regaining%20consciousness%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20nearby%20hospital.%20Reportedly%2C%20one%20of%20his%20first%20requests%20after%20regaining%20consciousness%20was%20to%20have%20his%20boots%20removed%2C%20as%20he%20believed%20he%20might%20never%20need%20them%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExactly%20three%20years%20later%2C%20on%20June%2016%2C%20Christian%20Eriksen%20returned%20to%20play%20in%20the%20ongoing%20edition%20of%20the%20Euro%20Football%20tournament%2C%20donning%20the%20national%20jersey%20once%20more.%20In%20the%2017th%20minute%2C%20a%20miracle%20happened%20as%20Eriksen%20scored%20the%20first%20goal%20for%20his%20team%2C%20reportedly%20wearing%20the%20same%20boots%20from%20that%20fateful%20day.%20It%20was%20like%20a%20fairytale%20we%20expect%20to%20happen%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20isn't%20a%20miracle%2C%20what%20is%3F%20These%20are%20the%20moments%20that%20give%20us%20hope%2C%20showing%20that%20bouncing%20back%20from%20the%20brink%20is%20always%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHoping%20Through%20Dark%20Times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20the%20same%20sense%20of%20awe%20while%20watching%20the%20Netflix%20movie%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Swimmers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20based%20on%20the%20true%20story%20of%20two%20Syrian%20girls%2C%20Yusra%20Mardini%20and%20her%20elder%20sister%2C%20Sara%20Mardini.%20Residents%20of%20Damascus%2C%20the%20sisters%20dreamt%20of%20representing%20their%20country%20in%20the%20Olympics.%20But%20Syria's%20civil%20war%20made%20it%20nearly%20impossible.%20Their%20push%20came%20when%20a%20bomb%20hit%20a%20venue%20where%20they%20were%20competing%20in%20a%20swimming%20competition.%20With%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20seek%20asylum%20as%20refugees%20in%20Germany%2C%20they%20embarked%20on%20a%20daunting%20journey%20without%20knowing%20how%20to%20reach%20their%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndeterred%20by%20the%20challenges%20ahead%2C%20the%20sisters%2C%20along%20with%20a%20relative%2C%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20as%20nerve-wracking%20as%20it%20could%20be.%20While%20their%20flight%20to%20Turkey%20was%20smooth%2C%20what%20followed%20tested%20even%20the%20toughest%20nerves.%20Local%20guides%20facilitating%20illegal%20migration%20suggested%20they%20take%20a%20boat%20to%20Greece%2C%20the%20shortest%20route%20to%20mainland%20Europe.%20During%20the%20perilous%20sea%20crossing%20from%20Turkey%2C%20their%20dinghy's%20engine%20failed.%20The%20sisters%20were%20among%20those%20who%20jumped%20into%20the%20water%2C%20guiding%20the%20overcrowded%20boat%20to%20safety%20and%20saving%20all%20on%20board%2C%20as%20documented%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3ETime%3C%2Fem%3E%20article.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20imagine%3A%20two%20little%20girls%20in%20an%20overcrowded%20dinghy%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20sinking%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20sea.%20Darkness%20surrounded%20them%2C%20with%20no%20clue%20how%20far%20the%20shore%20lay.%20Who%20could%20muster%20the%20courage%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20swim%20for%20three%20and%20a%20half%20hours%2C%20and%20guide%20the%20boat%20to%20safety%3F%20Most%20would%20have%20fainted.%20But%20not%20the%20Mardini%20sisters.%20They%20were%20fully%20aware%20that%20reaching%20shore%20didn't%20guarantee%20safety%3B%20as%20illegal%20refugees%2C%20they%20risked%20detention%20at%20any%20moment.%20Yet%2C%20driven%20by%20their%20Olympic%20dreams%2C%20they%20endured%20all%20and%20were%20prepared%20to%20face%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20long%20and%20arduous%20journey%20eventually%20led%20them%20to%20Germany.%20As%20they%20say%2C%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%20Within%20a%20year%20of%20arriving%20in%20Germany%2C%20Yusra%2C%20the%20younger%20and%20the%20more%20passionate%20one%20about%20swimming%2C%20qualified%20for%20the%20Rio%20Olympics%20as%20part%20of%20the%20refugee%20team.%20Now%20retired%2C%20she%20serves%20as%20a%20UNHCR%20Goodwill%20Ambassador%20and%20will%20be%20in%20Paris%2C%20cheering%20on%20refugees%20from%20around%20the%20world%20when%20the%20city%20hosts%20the%20Summer%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20the%20stories%20of%20Eriksen%20and%20Yusra%20have%20in%20common%3F%20Perhaps%20it's%20the%20determination%20to%20succeed%20against%20all%20odds.%20They%20possessed%20strength%20of%20character%20and%20found%20their%20way%20through%20the%20most%20challenging%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20own%20experience%2C%20when%20faced%20with%20adversity%2C%20saviours%20often%20emerge%20from%20unexpected%20places.%20For%20Yusra%2C%20it%20was%20a%20German%20swimming%20coach%20who%20helped%20her%20realise%20her%20Olympic%20dream.%20For%20Eriksen%2C%20it%20was%20the%20immediate%20support%20from%20his%20teammates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20life%2C%20I've%20had%20many%20saviours%20who%20helped%20me%20navigate%20difficult%20times.%20My%20humble%20advice%20to%20all%20of%20you%20is%20to%20never%20give%20up.%20Keep%20moving%20forward.%20Miracles%20do%20happen%20-%20and%20they%20happen%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mayank%20Mishra%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718871360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F1v6emba_yusra-mardini_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fmardini-sisters-and-eriksen-two-stories-that-prove-miracles-happen-all-the-time-5929893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20faced%20with%20adversity%2C%20saviours%20often%20emerge%20from%20unexpected%20places.%20For%20Yusra%2C%20it%20was%20a%20German%20swimming%20coach%20who%20helped%20her%20realise%20her%20Olympic%20dream.%20For%20Eriksen%2C%20it%20was%20the%20immediate%20support%20from%20his%20teammates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fmardini-sisters-and-eriksen-two-stories-that-prove-miracles-happen-all-the-time-5929893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fmardini-sisters-and-eriksen-two-stories-that-prove-miracles-happen-all-the-time-5929893%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fmardini-sisters-and-eriksen-two-stories-that-prove-miracles-happen-all-the-time-5929893%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ola%20Electric%20receives%20Sebi%20approval%20for%20IPO%3B%20looks%20to%20raise%20Rs%205%2C500%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718871219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F24%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1682316307-8621.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Fola-electric-receives-sebi-approval-for-ipo-looks-to-raise-rs-5-500-crore-124062000429_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ola%20Electric