TI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20submitted%20that%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20reservation%20laws%20were%20violative%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20After%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20court%20had%20reserved%20its%20judgement%20in%20March.%20Today%2C%20the%20final%20order%20has%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20days%20after%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20unanimously%20passed%20the%20reservation%20Bill%2C%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20had%20issued%20gazette%20notifications%20for%20raising%20the%20quota%20for%20deprived%20castes%20from%2050%20to%2065%20per%20cent%20in%20state%20government%20jobs%20and%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20JDU%20leader%20and%20minister%20Ashok%20Choudhary%20said%20the%20state%20government%20will%20study%20the%20judgment%20and%20challenge%20it%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20high%20court%20ruling%2C%20RJD's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Jha%20said%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20development.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20rulings%20prolong%20the%20journey%20towards%20the%20destination%20of%20social%20justice.%20We%20remember%20Tamil%20Nadu%20had%20to%20struggle%20for%20many%20years%2C%20we%20will%20do%20the%20same.%20But%20we%20must%20see%20what%20is%20the%20social%20background%20of%20these%20petitioners%2C%20who%20is%20controlling%20them%20from%20behind%20the%20curtains.%20We%20saw%20the%20same%20thing%20during%20the%20caste%20survey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RJD%20leader%20stressed%20the%20party's%20demand%20to%20put%20reservation%20under%20the%20ninth%20schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20shield%20it%20from%20court%20orders.%20%26quot%3BThe%20NDA%20government%20is%20in%20power%20now%2C%20courtesy%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20He%20should%20go%20to%20the%20higher%20court%20and%20secure%20the%20rights%20of%20a%20big%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718871180000%2C