%20to%20fall.%3Cp%3Enew%20look%20casting%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECentral%20banks%20from%20advanced%20economies%20plan%20to%20buy%20more%20gold%2C%20a%20World%20Gold%20Council%20survey%20indicates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20they%20were%20loading%20up%20on%20gold%20to%20hedge%20against%20risks%20such%20as%20inflation%20and%20economic%20shocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20central%20banks%20said%20they%20expected%20the%20US%20dollar's%20share%20in%20global%20reserves%20to%20fall%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEmerging%20economies%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-china-allied-central-banks-hoard-gold-dollar-weaponization-record-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20and%20its%20allies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20been%20hoarding%20gold%20to%20diversify%20from%20the%20US%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they're%20not%20the%20only%20gold%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20central%20banks%20from%20advanced%20economies%20are%20planning%20to%20load%20up%20on%20gold%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gold.org%2Fgoldhub%2Fdata%2F2024-central-bank-gold-reserves-survey%23from-login%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Gold%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%20survey%20released%20on%20Monday%20indicates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20yellow%20metal%20has%20come%20even%20though%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Frealtime-chart%2Fgold-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espot%20gold%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20hovering%20at%20record%20levels%2C%20about%20%242%2C330%20an%20ounce%2C%20after%20hitting%20nearly%20%242%2C450%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WGC%20survey%2C%20conducted%20from%20February%20to%20April%2C%20found%20that%2029%25%20of%2070%20central%20banks%20%E2%80%94%20the%20biggest%20share%20the%20WGC%20has%20observed%20since%202019%20%E2%80%94%20were%20planning%20to%20buy%20gold%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20central%20banks%2C%20about%2015%25%20of%20those%20in%20advanced%20economies%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20do%20so%20%E2%80%94%20also%20the%20most%20since%202019.%20Meanwhile%2C%20about%2040%25%20of%20emerging-market%20central%20banks%20said%20they'd%20be%20buying%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20banks'%20key%20reasons%20for%20more%20gold%20purchases%20included%20rebalancing%20their%20reserves%20and%20hedging%20against%20risks%20such%20as%20rising%20inflation%2C%20US%20dollar%20exposure%2C%20and%20market%20instability.%20Eight%20out%20of%20the%2020%20central%20banks%20that%20said%20they%20were%20planning%20to%20buy%20more%20gold%20also%20cited%20higher%20economic%20risks%20in%20countries%20where%20reserve%20currencies%20are%20from%20because%20of%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20rising%20US%20budget%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20their%20enthusiasm%20for%20gold%2C%2056%25%20of%20central%20banks%20from%20advanced%20economies%20said%20they%20expected%20the%20dollar's%20share%20of%20global%20reserves%20to%20fall%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20Nearly%20two-thirds%20of%20central%20banks%20from%20emerging%20economies%20expected%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4c4ed3f-5cbb-4c78-9fc2-1f6e70265780%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShrinking%20US%20dollar%20reserves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WGC's%20annual%20survey%20reflects%20the%20sentiment%20of%20central%20banks%20amid%20intense%20discussion%20about%20the%20dollar's%20dominant%20role%20as%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20has%20been%20gaining%20ground%20following%20the%20West's%20sweeping%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20over%20its%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20Other%20countries%20worried%20that%20they%2C%20too%2C%20could%20be%20locked%20out%20of%20the%20US-dollar-based%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20king%20dollar%20is%20so%20entrenched%20and%20pervasive%20in%20the%20world's%20financial%20system%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fde-dollarization-dollar-war-currency-usd-dominance-china-yuan-economy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Every%20few%20people%20think%20it%20can%20be%20dethroned%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-russia-actively-working-brics-local-currencies-platform-us-dollar-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20group%20of%20major%20emerging%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20working%20on%20a%20way%20around%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20dollar%20is%20still%20by%20far%20the%20most%20dominant%20currency%20in%20the%20foreign-exchange%20reserves%20of%20the%20world's%20central%20banks%2C%20the%20greenback's%20share%20in%20these%20reserves%20%E2%80%94%20after%20exchange-rate%20and%20interest-rate%20adjustments%20%E2%80%94%20declined%20from%20more%20than%2070%25%20in%202000%20to%20about%2055%25%20in%20the%20last%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.imf.org%2F%3Fsk%3De6a5f467-c14b-4aa8-9f6d-5a09ec4e62a4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInternational%20Monetary%20Fund%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20termed%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20US%20dollar's%20share%20of%20global%20reserves%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-imf-stealth-erosion-global-us-dollar-forex-reserves-sanctions-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estealth%20erosion%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-rich-countries-advanced-economies-buy-gold-dollar-share-reserves-2024-6%