%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvidya-balan-showers-love-on-bhool-bhulaiyaa-3-co-star-kartik-aaryan-for-chandu-champion-calls-it-gripping-and-engaging%2Farticleshow%2F111133036.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DP%20glams%20up%20in%20Rs%2053%20lakh%20Cartier%20jewelry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718867687000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111132858%2Cimgsize-49248.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-glams-up-with-1-16-crore-cartier-jewelry-for-the-kalki-2898-ad-event%2Farticleshow%2F111132858.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111132858.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDeepika%20Padukone%20recently%20turned%20heads%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20pre-release%20event%20for%20the%20upcoming%20sci-fi%20epic%20Kalki%202898%20AD.%20The%20event's%20theme%20seemed%20to%20be%20dark%2C%20with%20most%20of%20the%20stars%20wearing%20dark%20or%20black-colored%20outfits.%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BPadukone%20opted%20for%20a%20stunning%20Loewe%20Anagram%20Pebble%20Dress%20and%20exquisite%20Cartier%20jewelry%2C%20which%20included%20a%20trio%20of%20diamond%20bracelets.%20The%20most%20captivating%20piece%20was%20the%20Panth%C3%A8re%20de%20Cartier%20bracelet%2C%20crafted%20from%2018K%20white%20gold%20and%20adorned%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-glams-up-with-1-16-crore-cartier-jewelry-for-the-kalki-2898-ad-event%2Farticleshow%2F111132858.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Man's%20Genitals%20Removed%2C%20Sex-Change%20Surgery%20Done%20While%20He%20Was%20Sleeping%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20to%20bed%20as%20a%20man%20but%20woke%20up%20as%20a%20woman.%20For%2020-year-old%20Mujahid%2C%20life%20took%20a%20drastic%20turn%20when%20he%20was%20deceived%20into%20undergoing%20gender%20reassignment%20surgery.%20This%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20another%20man%20in%20collusion%20with%20doctors%20from%20a%20local%20medical%20college%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sensational%20case%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20and%20led%20to%20protests%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(BKU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20Begrajpur%20Medical%20College%20in%20Mansoorpur.%20Mujahid%2C%2020%20and%20resident%20of%20Sanjak%20village%2C%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20deceived%20by%20Omprakash%20on%20June%203.%20Omprakash%20allegedly%20convinced%20the%20doctors%20at%20the%20medical%20college%20to%20perform%20surgery%20on%20Mujahid%2C%20which%20involved%20the%20removal%20of%20his%20genitals%20and%20a%20forced%20gender%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMujahid%20claims%20that%20Omprakash%20had%20been%20threatening%20and%20harassing%20him%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20Mujahid%20was%20falsely%20told%20that%20he%20had%20a%20medical%20issue%20requiring%20hospital%20inspection.%20Accompanied%20by%20Omprakash%2C%20he%20visited%20the%20facility%20where%20the%20hospital%20staff%20allegedly%20administered%20anaesthesia%20and%20performed%20the%20sex-change%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20brought%20me%20here%2C%20and%20the%20next%20morning%20I%20had%20an%20operation.%20When%20I%20regained%20consciousness%2C%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20had%20been%20changed%20from%20a%20boy%20to%20a%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20Mujahid%20recounted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmprakash%20allegedly%20told%20him%20that%20he%20would%20now%20have%20to%20live%20with%20him%2C%20adding%20that%20no%20one%20from%20his%20family%20or%20community%20would%20accept%20him%20anymore.%20Omprakash%20also%20threatened%20to%20shoot%20Mujahid's%20father%20and%20seize%20his%20share%20of%20the%20family%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'I%20changed%20you%20from%20a%20man%20to%20a%20woman%20and%20now%20you%20have%20to%20live%20with%20me.%20I%20have%20prepared%20a%20lawyer%20and%20prepared%20a%20court%20marriage%20for%20you.%20Now%20I%20will%20shoot%20your%20father%20and%20the%20land%20of%20your%20share%20will%20be%20named%20after%20me%20and%20then%20I%20will%20sell%20it%20and%20go%20to%20Lucknow'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mujahid%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20BKU%20workers%2C%20led%20by%20farmer%20leader%20Shyam%20Pal%2C%20staged%20a%20protest%20at%20the%20medical%20college%2C%20demanding%20immediate%20action%20against%20Omprakash%20and%20the%20involved%20doctors.%20The%20police%20have%20assured%20the%20demonstrators%20that%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20would%20be%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Shyam%20Pal%2C%20this%20incident%20points%20to%20a%20larger%20issue%20of%20organ%20trafficking%20in%20the%20hospital.%20He%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20racket%20operating%20within%20the%20hospital%20that%20targets%20individuals%20for%20organ%20harvesting%20and%20gender%20reassignment%20without%20consent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20We%20want%20this%20illegal%20business%20of%20selling%20body%20parts%20to%20be%20stopped%20immediately.%20All%20those%20involved%2C%20including%20the%20hospital%20management%20and%20those%20who%20facilitated%20this%20crime%2C%20should%20be%20held%20accountable%20and%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pal%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pal%20said%20that%20Mujahid's%20father%20had%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20on%20June%2016%2C%20which%20led%20to%20Omprakash's%20arrest.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Pal%20criticised%20the%20police%20for%20their%20lax%20attitude%20and%20called%20for%20stricter%20action.%20He%20also%20demanded%20compensation%20of%20at%20least%20Rs%202%20crore%20for%20Mujahid%2C%20whose%20life%20has%20been%20severely%20affected%20by%20this%20traumatic%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20family%20and%20the%20protestors%20will%20be%20thoroughly%20investigated%2C%20and%20appropriate%20legal%20actions%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20found%20guilty%2C%26quot%3B%20Senior%20Muzaffarnagar%20police%20officer%20Ramashish%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20arresting%20Omprakash%2C%20the%20police%20are%20also%20investigating%20the%20hospital%20staff%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718867520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fdu0tfgj_surgery-generic-afp_625x300_11_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-mans-genitals-removed-sex-change-surgery-done-while-he-was-sleeping-5929531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20went%20to%20bed%20as%20a%20man%20but%20woke%20up%20as%20a%20woman.%20For%2020-year-old%20Mujahid%2C%20life%20took%20a%20drastic%20turn%20when%20he%20was%20deceived%20into%20undergoing%20gender%20reassignment%20surgery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-mans-genitals-removed-sex-change-surgery-done-while-he-was-sleeping-5929531%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-mans-genitals-removed-sex-change-surgery-done-while-he-was-sleeping-5929531%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-mans-genitals-removed-sex-change-surgery-done-while-he-was-sleeping-5929531%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fin%20min%20imposes%20Rs%2018.82cr%20penalty%20on%20world's%20largest%20crypto%20exchange%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718867442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111132776%2Cimgsize-55446.c