ribing%20the%20film%20as%20'outstanding'%20and%20praising%20Kartik%20Aaryan%2C%20Kabir%20Khan%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20team%20with%20heartfelt%20emojis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkartik-aaryan-comforts-emotional-fan-with-humour-roti-kaiko-hai-at-chandu-champion-event%2Farticleshow%2F111131632.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20Sailors%20Wield%20Knives%2C%20Axe%20In%20Disputed%20Sea%20Clash%20With%20Philippines%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChinese%20coast%20guard%20sailors%20brandishing%20knives%2C%20an%20axe%20and%20other%20weapons%20clashed%20with%20Philippine%20naval%20vessels%20near%20a%20strategic%20reef%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20dramatic%20new%20footage%20released%20by%20Manila%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clash%20took%20place%20Monday%20as%20Philippine%20forces%20attempted%20to%20resupply%20marines%20stationed%20on%20a%20derelict%20warship%2C%20the%20Sierra%20Madre%2C%20deliberately%20grounded%20atop%20the%20disputed%20Second%20Thomas%20Shoal%2C%20Manila%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20escalating%20confrontations%20between%20Chinese%20and%20Philippine%20ships%20in%20recent%20months%20as%20Beijing%20steps%20up%20efforts%20to%20push%20its%20claims%20to%20the%20disputed%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20footage%20of%20the%20confrontation%20released%20late%20Wednesday%20by%20the%20Philippine%20military%20showed%20small%20boats%20crewed%20by%20Chinese%20sailors%20shouting%2C%20waving%20knives%20and%20using%20sticks%20to%20hit%20an%20inflatable%20boat%20as%20a%20siren%20blares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Philippines%20military%20said%20the%20axe-wielding%20sailor%20had%20%26quot%3Bthreatened%20to%20injure%26quot%3B%20a%20Filipino%20soldier%2C%20while%20others%20were%20%26quot%3Bexplicitly%20threatening%20to%20harm%26quot%3B%20Filipino%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Filipino%20sailor%20lost%20a%20thumb%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20Chinese%20coast%20guard%20confiscate%20or%20destroy%20Philippine%20equipment%20including%20guns%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Philippine%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManila's%20footage%20of%20the%20clash%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20photos%20released%20by%20Beijing's%20state%20media%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20did%20not%20show%20Chinese%20forces%20wielding%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20insisted%20that%20its%20coast%20guard%20behaved%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%20and%20restrained%26quot%3B%20way%20during%20the%20confrontation%20and%20claimed%20%26quot%3Bno%20direct%20measures%26quot%3B%20were%20taken%20against%20Filipino%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20clip%20shared%20by%20Manila%2C%20a%20Chinese%20sailor%20standing%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20one%20of%20the%20boats%20can%20be%20clearly%20seen%20waving%20an%20axe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20clip%20shows%20a%20Chinese%20coast%20guard%20sailor%20violently%20striking%20the%20inflatable%20boat%20with%20a%20stick.%20A%20second%20man%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20stabbing%20the%20boat%20with%20a%20knife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(Chinese%20coast%20guard)%20personnel%20then%20began%20hurling%20rocks%20and%20other%20objects%20at%20our%20personnel%2C%26quot%3B%20Manila%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20slashed%20the%20(inflatable%20boats)%2C%20rendering%20them%20inoperable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Filipino%20sailors%2C%20clad%20in%20brown%20camouflage%20with%20helmets%20and%20vests%2C%20are%20not%20carrying%20weapons%20in%20the%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmidst%20this%20violent%20confrontation%2C%20the%20CCG%20(Chinese%20coast%20guard)%20also%20deployed%20tear%20gas%2C%20intensifying%20the%20chaos%20and%20confusion%2C%20while%20continuously%20blaring%20sirens%20to%20further%20disrupt%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20caption%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilippine%20military%20chief%20General%20Romeo%20Brawner%20said%20Wednesday%20the%20outnumbered%20Filipino%20crew%20had%20been%20unarmed%20and%20had%20fought%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bbare%20hands%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20clip%2C%20a%20voice%20speaking%20Tagalog%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20someone%20had%20%26quot%3Blost%20a%20finger%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManila%20has%20accused%20Beijing%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bact%20of%20piracy%26quot%3B%20against%20its%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20demanded%20the%20return%20of%20items%20%26quot%3Blooted%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side%2C%20including%20seven%20guns%2C%20and%20reparations%20for%20the%20damaged%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Perilous'%20situation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20Beijing%20is%20escalating%20confrontations%20with%20the%20Philippines%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20push%20it%20out%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20armed%20attack%26quot%3B%20against%20Philippine%20public%20vessels%2C%20aircraft%2C%20armed%20forces%20and%20coastguard%20anywhere%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20would%20invoke%20a%20mutual%20defense%20treaty%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20call%20Wednesday%20with%20Philippine%20counterpart%20Enrique%20A.%20Manalo%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20%26quot%3Bemphasized%20that%20the%20(China's)%20actions%20undermine%20regional%20peace%20and%20stability%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20the%20State%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20%26quot%3Bunderscored%20the%20United%20States'%20ironclad%20commitments%20to%20the%20Philippines%20under%20our%20Mutual%20Defense%20Treaty%26quot%3B%2C%20Blinken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20analyst%20told%20AFP%20this%20week's%20clashes%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20