2cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Bombay%20Fines%20Students%20Rs%201.2%20Lakh%20Each%20Over%20Ramayana%20Skit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Bombay%20has%20fined%20eight%20students%20for%20staging%20a%20controversial%20play%20titled%20'Raahovan%2C'%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20parody%20of%20Ramayana%2C%20during%20the%20institute's%20Performing%20Arts%20Festival%20(PAF)%20on%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20students%20had%20formally%20complained%20against%20the%20play%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20loosely%20based%20on%20the%20revered%20Hindu%20epic%20Ramayana%20and%20had%20derogatory%20references%20to%20Hindu%20beliefs%20and%20deities.%20Some%20students%20alleged%20that%20the%20play%20lampooned%20the%20lead%20characters%20and%20mocked%20cultural%20values%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20%26quot%3Bpromoting%20feminism%26quot%3B.%20The%20complaints%20led%20to%20a%20disciplinary%20committee%20meeting%20on%20May%208%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20penalties%20announced%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20imposed%20fines%20of%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20each%20on%20four%20students%20-%20the%20amount%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20a%20semester's%20tuition%20fee.%20Four%20other%20students%20were%20fined%20Rs%2040%2C000%20each.%20Graduating%20students%20faced%20additional%20sanctions%2C%20including%20a%20ban%20from%20the%20institute's%20gymkhana%20awards%20given%20to%20students.%20Junior%20students%20were%20debarred%20from%20hostel%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20penalties%20are%20due%20on%20July%2020%2C%202024%2C%20at%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Dean%20of%20Student%20Affairs.%20The%20institute%20warned%20that%20any%20breach%20of%20this%20penalty%20would%20result%20in%20further%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20gained%20traction%20on%20social%20media%20when%20the%20'IIT%20B%20for%20Bharat'%20group%20denounced%20the%20play%20on%20April%208%2C%20citing%20it%20as%20a%20mockery%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20the%20Ramayana.%20The%20group%20posted%20video%20clips%20from%20the%20performance%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20students%20misused%20academic%20freedom%20to%20ridicule%20revered%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20show%20students%20presenting%20a%20play%20allegedly%20inspired%20by%20Ramayana%20characters%20and%20plot%20settings.%20In%20one%20video%2C%20a%20student%2C%20allegedly%20playing%20Sita%2C%20praises%20her%20%26quot%3Bkidnapper%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20place%20she%20was%20taken%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20the%20disciplinary%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20IIT%20Bombay%20administration%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20play%20'Raahovan%2C'%20which%20depicted%20the%20Ramayana%20in%20a%20derogatory%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20stated%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%20%26quot%3BWe%20urge%20the%20administration%20to%20establish%20guidelines%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20religion%20is%20ridiculed%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%20on%20campus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20certain%20groups%20appreciated%20the%20institution's%20decision%20to%20initiate%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20the%20students%2C%20some%20have%20condemned%20it%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20always%20heard%20that%20educational%20institutions%20should%20be%20safe%20spaces%2C%20safe%20for%20voicing%20opinions.%20Alas%2C%20even%20IITs%20are%20no%20longer%20safe%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20person%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20egregious.%20Students%20cannot%20be%20fined%20in%20colleges%20for%20being%20disrespectful%20to%20any%20religion.%20Colleges%20are%20places%20where%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20freely%20mock%20religion.%20IIT%20Bombay%20must%20take%20this%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Performing%20Arts%20Festival%20is%20an%20annual%20cultural%20event%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20known%20for%20showcasing%20student%20talent%20in%20various%20art%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718864700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fo58dr6qg_iit-bombay-raahovan-_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Bombay%20has%20fined%20eight%20students%20for%20staging%20a%20controversial%20play%20titled%20'Raahovan%2C'%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20parody%20of%20Ramayana%2C%20during%20the%20institute's%20Performing%20Arts%20Festival%20(PAF)%20on%20March%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Is%20The%20End%20Of%20The%20US-Saudi%20Petro%20Deal%20An%20Opportunity%20For%20India%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.assettype.com%2Fbqprimehindi%252Fimport%252F2023-12%252Fus-dollars-generic-pixabay_650x400_61523930029.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%252Ccompress%26fmt%3Dwebp%26w%3D732%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20event%20occurred%20last%20week.%20Its%20impact%20may%20not%20be%20felt%20immediately%2C%20but%20with%20time%2C%20it%20will%20be.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20did%20not%20renew%20the%2050-year-old%20pact%20with%20the%20US%20on%20the%20petro-dollar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20Of%20The%20Agreement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%201974%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20third%20Arab-Israel%20war%20when%20the%20Arabs%20had%20weaponised%20their%20oil%20resources%20and%20announced%20an%20oil%20embargo.%20To%20hedge%20against%20this%20weaponisation%20of%20the%20future's%20'black%20gold'%2C%20in%20June%201974%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20set%20up%20a%20joint%20commission%20for%20economic%20cooperation.%20The%20commission%20was%20authorised%20to%20facilitate%20Saudi%20spending%20on%20US%20dollars.%20Both%20sides%20concluded%20a%20pact%2C%20whereby%20the%20pricing%20of%20crude%20became%20pegged%20to%20the%20US%20dollar.%20This%20strengthened%20the%20dollar%2C%20giving%20it%20heft%20and%20an%20edge%20over%20all%20other%20currencies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20something%20that%20still%20underpins%20the%20existing%20global%20economic%20order.%20The%20Saudis%20also%20committed%20to%20investing%20surplus%20funds%20into%20US%20bonds%20in%20exchange%20for%20military%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20pact%20did%20not%20mean%20that%20Saudis%20would%20sell%20oil%20in%20dollars%20alone%2C%20the%20emerging%20arrangement%20-%20the%20agreement%20to%20invest%20in%20US%20Treasury%20bonds%20-%20was%20a%20secret%20one%2C%20details%20of%20which%20emerged%20later.%20It%20translated%20into%20crude%20being%20not%20only%20priced%20but%20also%20sold%20exclusively%20in%20US%20dollars.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20year%2C%20the%20pact%20was%20not%20renewed.%20This%20has%20sparked%20off%20great%20jubilation%2C%20on%20one%20hand%2C%20about%20the%20dollar's%20imminent%20demise.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20have%20dismissed%20it%20as%20being%20of%20no%20consequence.%20The%20truth%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20lies%20somewhere%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Move%20Towards%20De-dollarisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20unintended%20consequence%20of%20the%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%20for%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20including%20cutting%20it%20off%20from%20the%20international%20SWIFT%20system%2C%20has%20been%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20slow%20but%20sure%20process%20of%20de-dollarisation%20in%20the%20world.%20In%20order%20to%20hedge%20against%20such%20sanctions%2C%20a%20number%20of%20countries%20-%20mainly%20emerging%20economies%20-%20have%20begun%20using%20local%20currencies%20for%20bilateral%20trade.%20India%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20been%20using%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20for%20trade%20with%20Russia.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20made%20its%20first%20purchases%20of%20crude%20oil%20from%20the%20UAE%20in%20INR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhu%20Nainan%2C%20the%20Editor%20of%20Petrowatch%2C%20however%2C%20warns%20that%20the%20probable%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20Saudi%20action%20could%20be%20the%20yuan%2C%20given%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20China%20has%20emerged%20as%20not%20only%20the%20largest%20crude%20importer%20of%20the%20Saudis%20but%20also%20its%20largest%20trading%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20Yuan%20Can't%20Be%20Ignored%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20the%20largest%20buyer%20of%20crude%20oil%20in%20the%20world.%20Data%20for%202022%20shows%20that%20Saudis%20exported%20crude%20to%20China%20worth%20%2456.1%20billion.%20India%20came%20in%20third%2C%20importing%20Saudi%20crude%20worth%20%2432.7%20billion.%20%C2%A0At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20total%20trade%20turnover%20between%20China%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20was%20%24106%20billion.%20Of%20this%2C%20Chinese%20exports%20to%20the%20kingdom%20accounted%20for%20%2436.5%20billion.%20This%20is%20set%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20US-China%20rivalry%20increased%2C%20China%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20the%20yuan%20for%20its%20external%20trade%2C%20including%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20In%202023%2C%20China%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20signed%20a%20local%20currency%20swap%20agreement%20worth%20%247%20billion%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20boost%20trade%20using%20their%20currencies%20and%20reduce%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20dollar.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20year%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20signed%20on%20to%20the%20mBridge%20project%2C%20launched%20in%202021%20between%20the%20central%20banks%20of%20China%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Thailand%20and%20the%20UAE%20to%20develop%20a%20new%20system%20for%20cross-border%20payments%20using%20central%20bank%20digital%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran-Saudi%20truce%20brokered%20by%20China%20last%20year%20further%20increased%20its%20footprint%20in%20the%20region%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20along%20with%20the%20UAE%20and%20four%20more%20countries%2C%20signalled%20its%20interest%20in%20joining%20the%20BRICS%20grouping%20of%20countries.%20The%20BRICS%20is%20in%20discussions%20for%20an%20alternate%20trading%20currency%2C%20with%20a%20number%20of%20member-states%20having%20initiated%20trade%20in%20local%20currency%20between%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20Saudi%20decision%2C%20while%20not%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20substantial%20role%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20will%20definitely%20add%20to%20the%20de-dollarisation%20process%20underway%20in%20international%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Opportunity%20For%20The%20Indian%20Rupee%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20all%20this%20mean%20for%20India%3F%20India%20has%20ambitions%20of%20making%20the%20INR%20go%20international.%20It%20has%20already%20been%20trading%20with%20Russia%20in%20rupees.%20More%20recently%2C%20it%20entered%20into%20a%20local%20currency%20trade%20agreement%20with%20the%20UAE%20and%20has%20made%20its%20first%20oil%20purchases%20in%20INR.%20It%20is%20in%20discussions%20with%20Singapore%20for%20local%20currency%20settlement%2C%20which%20can%20then%20extend%20to%20the%20ASEAN%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20now%20also%20trying%20to%20diversify%20its%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves.%20Currently%2C%20as%20per%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20data%2C%20India's%20overall%20exchange%20reserves%20stood%20at%20nearly%20%24641%20billion%20as%20of%20May%203%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20which%20is%20held%20in%20US%20Dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20recent%20event%2C%20RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20priority%20is%20to%20diversify%20our%20deployment%20of%20forex%20reserves%20in%20more%20currencies%20and%20different%20types%20of%20assets%2C%20particularly%20gold.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20how%20the%20lapse%20of%20the%20petro-dollar%20deal%20will%20impact%20India%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20India's%20trade%20volumes%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%20are%20nowhere%20near%20China's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20for%202023%20reveals%20that%20bilateral%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20grown%20and%20stood%20at%20a%20total%20turnover%20of%20%2452.76%20billion.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20India's%20imports%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20were%20%2442.03%20billion%20and%20exports%20%2410.72%20billion.%20With%20the%20balance%20of%20trade%20so%20heavily%20tilted%20towards%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20it%20is%20doubtful%20whether%20India%20can%20clinch%20a%20deal%20for%20paying%20for%20Saudi%20crude%20in%20INR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimited%20Possibilities%2C%20For%20Now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20it%20in%20perspective%2C%20while%20India%20pays%20for%20Russian%20crude%20in%20INR%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20problem%20with%20billions%20of%20rupees%20accumulating%20in%20Indian%20banks%2C%20with%20nothing%20for%20Russia%20to%20spend%20it%20on.%20If%2C%20however%2C%20India%20is%20able%20to%20accelerate%20its%20manufacturing%20base%20and%20increase%20exports%2C%20then%20a%20deal%20may%20be%20possible.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNeither%20will%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20petro-dollar%20deal%20impact%20the%20price%20of%20oil%20on%20the%20global%20market%2C%20as%20it%20will%20be%20pegged%20to%20supply%20and%20demand.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Saudi%20rial%20remains%20pegged%20to%20the%20US%20dollar.%20Also%2C%20both%20the%20US%20and%20Saudis%20are%20reported%20to%20be%20negotiating%20a%20new%20security%20pack%2C%20whereby%20the%20central%20role%20of%20the%20dollar%20will%20again%20be%20reinforced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20like%20many%20other%20countries%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20diversify%20its%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20and%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20the%20US%20dollar.%20Thus%2C%20while%20the%20dollar%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20sway%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20the%20world%20without%20a%20doubt%20is%20moving%20towards%20an%20alternative%20currency.%20The%20lapse%20of%20the%20petro-dollar%20deal%20will%20act%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20this%20de-dollarisation%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Aditi%20Bhaduri%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718864640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.assettype.com%2Fbqprimehindi%252Fimport%252F2023-12%252Fus-dollars-generic-pixabay_650x400_61523930029.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-the-end-of-the-us-saudi-petro-deal-an-opportunity-for-india-5929169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20dollar%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20sway%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20the%20world%20without%20a%20doubt%20is%20moving%20towards%20an%20alternative%20currency.%20The%20lapse%20of%20the%20petro-dollar%20deal%20will%20act%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20this%20de-dollarisation%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%