f%20Education%20has%20ordered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fugc-net-neet-row-education-emergency-net-scrapped-amid-neet-row-opposition-gets-new-ammo-5928689%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3Ecancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20held.%20Controversy%20has%20again%20erupted%20following%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20second%20entrance%20exam%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA.%20The%20centre%20had%20earlier%20scrapped%C2%A0%20the%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%201%2C563%20candidates%20who%20took%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-ug-2024-result-row-top-rankers-reduced-to-61-as-grace-marks-withdrawn-5882844%5C%22%3ENEET%20UG%202024%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20re-test%20has%20been%20scheduled%20for%20these%20students%20for%20June%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20UGC-NET%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20conducts%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(UGC-NET)%20to%20screen%20eligible%20candidates%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20and%20PhD%20admissions%20in%20Indian%20universities%20and%20colleges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%2C%20this%20year%2C%20was%20held%20in%20pen%20and%20paper%20mode%20on%20June%2018%2C%202024%20in%20two%20shifts.%20The%20first%20shift%20was%20conducted%20from%209.30%20am%20to%2012.30%20pm%20and%20the%20second%20shift%20from%203%20pm%20to%206%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20regularise%20the%20UGC-NET%20examination%20cycle%2C%20the%20agency%20holds%20the%20UGC%20NET%20December%202023%20in%2083%20subjects%2C%20at%20selected%20cities%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20every%20year%20in%20the%20month%20of%20June%20and%20December.%20From%20December%202018%20onwards%2C%20UGC-NET%20was%20being%20held%20in%20Computer%20Based%20Test%20(CBT)%20mode.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20departure%20from%20previous%20practices%2C%20the%20exam%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20pen-and-paper%20format%20this%20time.%20Approximately%2081%25%20of%20the%2011.21%20lakh%20registered%20candidates%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20held%20in%20317%20cities%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20are%20required%20to%20score%20an%20aggregate%20marks%20in%20Paper%201%20and%20Paper%202%20of%20UGC%20NET%20for%20awarding%20of%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20(JRF)%20and%2F%20or%20eligibility%20for%20Assistant%20Professorship.%20Students%20who%20qualify%20the%20eligibility%20test%20for%20Assistant%20Professorship%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20concerned%20universities%2Fcolleges%2Fstate%20governments%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%20for%20recruitment%20of%20Assistant%20Professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidates%20qualifying%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor%20and%20admission%20to%20PhD'%20category%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor%20and%20admission%20to%20PhD%20but%20not%20for%20the%20award%20of%20JRF.%20Similarly%2C%20students%20qualifying%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98admission%20to%20PhD%20only'%20category%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20admission%20to%20PhD%20only%20but%20not%20for%20the%20award%20of%20JRF%20and%2For%20appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718861160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fqmf5uoto_csirugc-net-june-2024-_625x300_02_May_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhat-is-ugc-net-exam-and-why-is-it-conducted-5928819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20exam%20was%20held%20in%20pen%20and%20paper%20mode%20on%20June%2018%2C%202024%20in%20two%20shifts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https