%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Hetal%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20was%20when%20Hetals%E2%80%99s%20father%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20saw%20how%20passionate%20I%20was%20about%20sumo%20wrestling%20and%20decided%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20do%20this%20together.%20He%20bought%20me%20a%20laptop%2C%20and%20every%20day%2C%20we%20would%20watch%20videos%20on%20sumo%20wrestling%2C%20study%20the%20technique%2C%20and%20then%20practise.%20He%20and%20my%20brother%20would%20attempt%20the%20sport%20step%20by%20step%20and%20teach%20me.%20We%20followed%20this%20routine%20from%20morning%20to%20night%20for%20weeks.%20It%20became%20a%20sort%20of%20dance%2C%20there%20was%20a%20rhythm%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20were%20relentless%20in%20their%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20World%20Championship%20(2008)%20in%20Estonia%20were%20passing%20quickly%20and%20Hetal%20still%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20found%20a%20sponsor.%20Time%20was%20running%20out.%20But%2C%20as%20she%20emphasises%2C%20help%20always%20arrives%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20local%20Gujarati%20newspaper%20would%20often%20write%20about%20my%20achievements%2C%20and%20when%20I%20approached%20them%20with%20this%20dilemma%2C%20they%20put%20out%20an%20article%20asking%20if%20anyone%20would%20like%20to%20sponsor%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F193355%2Fnational-sports-day-pv-sindhu-greatest-moments-sports-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tournament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20many%20came%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20celebrated%20for%20my%20strength%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20teenager%2C%20the%20memory%20of%20standing%20on%20forei