EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20had%20spent%20the%20last%2025%20years%20in%20the%20water%20and%20energy%20industry%20developing%20hundreds%20of%20water%20treatment%20facilities%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Mansi%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CIncidentally%2C%20my%20father%20had%20been%20an%20engineer%20in%20the%20water%20and%20energy%20industry%20for%20over%2025%20years%2C%20and%20designed%20as%20well%20as%20operated%20over%20400%20wastewater%20treatment%20facilities%20in%20India%20with%20the%20consistent%20takeaway%20that%2075%25%20of%20these%20facilities%20failed%20operationally%20even%20though%20they%20were%20key%20to%20the%20local%20water%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201079px)%20100vw%2C%201079px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Water%20treatment%20by%20Digital%20Paani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270.jpg%201079w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-500x334.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352673%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManaging%20Water%20Treatment%20Infrastructure%3A%20Mansi%20Jain%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Digital%20Paani%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBut%20why%20do%20these%20facilities%20fail%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mansi%2C%20most%20of%20these%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20in%20the%20long%20run%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20including%20biological%20disturbance%2C%20equipment%20failure%20like%20burnt%20pumps%2C%20or%20the%20choking%20of%20membrane%20filters%20that%20act%20as%20a%20barrier%20to%20separate%20contaminants%20from%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20a%20way%20for%20these%20plants%20to%20anticipate%20these%20problems%20and%20fix%20them%20in%20advance%20to%20improve%20their%20efficiency%20and%20longevity%3F%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fstartup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20are%20developing%20technological%20solutions%20for%20wastewater%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20about%2090%2C000%20installed%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants.%20But%20today%2095%25%20of%20the%20market%20is%20managed%20entirely%20manually%20by%20deploying%20operators%20in%20each%20plant.%20This%20has%20several%20drawbacks%3B%20problems%20are%20detected%20about%20three%20weeks%20late%20after%20breakdowns%20and%20operators%20lack%20the%20expertise%20to%20tackle%20problems.%20Other%20technologies%20in%20the%20market%20only%20make%20dents%20in%20part%20of%20the%20problem%3B%20they%20only%20monitor%20data%20or%20automate%20the%20key%20equipment%20like%20pumps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20can%20solve%20this%20problem%20in%20a%20scalable%20manner%2C%20they%20started%20Digital%20Paani%20in%20end%202020%2C%20piloted%20an%20IoT-enabled%20software%20that%20manages%20end-to-end%20operations%20of%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%2C%20and%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cincredible%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20helping%20buildings%20and%20industries%20move%20towards%20water%20neutrality%20and%20reduce%20water%20losses%20across%20their%20campus.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20in%20a%20stepwise%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Maximise%20recycling%20by%20ensuring%20wastewater%20infrastructure%20is%20working%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Helping%20industries%20and%20residential%20societies%20do%20water%20accounting%20real-time%2C%20know%20where%20they%20are%20having%20water%20losses%2C%20and%20provide%20roadmaps%20to%20reduce%20those%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Actually%20reducing%20those%20losses%20by%20providing%20operational%20excellence%20and%20management%20through%20technology%20for%20key%20assets%20contributing%20to%20water%20losses%20such%20as%20cooling%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20is%20a%20water%20management%20platform%20that%20tracks%20and%20manages%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20performs%20tasks%20like%20equipment%20automation%2C%20providing%20WhatsApp%20updates%20to%20users%2C%20and%20guiding%20process%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20real-time%20insights%2C%20complete%20control%2C%20and%2024%2F7%20management%20with%20actionable%20recommendations%2C%20they%20drive%20operational%20excellence%20for%20sustainable%20water%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mansi%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20our%20platform%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20water%20infrastructure%2C%20telling%20buildings%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20with%20their%20infrastructure%20and%20what%20it%20needs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20providing%20the%20medicine%20to%20fix%20it%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20directing%20technicians%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344518%2Ffind-missing-children-raju-nepali-duars-express-mail-ngo-rescues-trafficked-children-counselling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20chemical%20dosage%20required%2C%20automating%20equipment%20to%20function%20properly%20or%20directing%20operators%20on%20the%20best%20next%20steps.%20Through%20our%20work%2C%20we%20help%20clients%20save%20crores%20in%20fines%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20they%20recycle%20their%20wastewater%20%E2%80%94%2090%20million%20litres%20of%20wastewater%20is%20treated%20daily%20at%20plants%20associated%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20over%2040%20industry%20giants%2C%20including%20Tata%20Power%2C%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20Britannia%2C%20and%20Leela%20Hotels%2C%20are%20using%20the%20Gurugram-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20do%20you%20treat%20water%20Digital%20Paani%20style%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-300x262.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-500x437.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-768x671.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-150x131.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352678%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20elements%20that%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20with%20to%20address%20their%20water%20treatment%20needs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnlocking%20business%20and%20product%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20log%20in%20design%20inputs%20about%20the%20infrastructure%20into%20our%20software%2C%20we%20create%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20for%20operating%20the%20plant%20in%20real-time.%20Our%20client%20can%20visualise%20the%20asset%20(wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%20and%20can%20gauge%20its%20analytics%20from%20how%20much%20wastewater%20is%20getting%20treated%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20treatment%20being%20achieved%20and%20whether%20the%20equipment%20is%20functioning%20properly%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mansi%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3moOD09wNk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20client%20has%20a%20complete%20online%20software%20before%20them%20to%20visualise%20their%20asset.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20inside%20the%20plant%2C%20our%20software%20can%20assess%20and%20interpret%20data%20using%20AI%20to%20detect%20it.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20clients%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20be%20on%20our%20software%20to%20manage%20these%20issues.%20Management%20actions%20are%20happening%20automatically%2C%20whether%20through%20equipment%20control%20or%20by%20telling%20operators%20directly%20what%20to%20do.%20Clients%20just%20receive%20alert%20notifications%20on%20their%20WhatsApp%20number%20to%20make%20things